~ hello.sprout  —  Your very first Sprout program! 🌱
~ ───────────────────────────────────────────────────

bloom "Hello, World! 🌍"
bloom "Welcome to Sprout!"
bloom ""

~ Ask the user for their name
harvest name with "What is your name? "
bloom "Hello, " + name + "! 🌟 Great to meet you!"

~ A little math
grow age as 10
bloom "In 5 years you will be " + (age + 5) + " years old."
